import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"getting-started"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#getting-started"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Getting started`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"mostly-automatic-install"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#mostly-automatic-install"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Mostly automatic install`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol"><MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`npm install react-native-share --save`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol"><MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`react-native link react-native-share`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
